On a flight from Los Angeles to Paris, a mad scientist on the run from the CIA is 

transporting a coffin containing the body of a colleague infected with a 

genetically modified virus. While the 747 crosses a violent thunderstorm, the 

instability of the aircraft allows the corpse to get out of its container. The 

flesh-eating zombie quickly starts to spread the virus, infecting many of the 

passengers which now will have to fight for their lives stranded in the air with 

no way out...
